パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.ast

インタフェース ASTHelper<T extends StructureNode>

型パラメータ:
T - subtype of StructureNode with which the AST helper works
既知の実装クラスのリスト:
JavaASTHelper
public interface ASTHelper<T extends StructureNode>
Handles language specific ASTs and provides access to their content. An AST helper is associated to a file.
作成者:
Beat Fluri, Giacomo Ghezzi

    • createMethodInClassHistory

      StructureEntityVersion createMethodInClassHistory​(ClassHistory classHistory, T node, java.lang.String version)
      Creates and returns the StructureEntityVersion as method of the ClassHistory. The method is attached to the corresponding MethodHistory, if exists. Otherwise a new one is created.
      パラメータ:
      classHistory - to create the structure entity version for
      node - to create the structure entity version
      version - the number or id of the version to create
      戻り値:
      the method structure entity version in the class history for the node

    • createInnerClassInClassHistory

      StructureEntityVersion createInnerClassInClassHistory​(ClassHistory classHistory, T node, java.lang.String version)

    • createDeclarationTree

      Node createDeclarationTree​(T node, java.lang.String qualifiedName)
      Creates and returns the declaration Node tree for the StructureNode. In addition it replaces the qualified name with the given one.
      パラメータ:
      node - to create the declaration tree
      qualifiedName - to use for the tree generation
      戻り値:
      the declaration tree for the structure node
